{"tid":1441274,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"執法壓力大 幾乎每年一宗自殺","createTime":"2019-08-10T15:32:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T16:12:10.000Z","uid":10616,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ec3c321a852a600c8bf76294edfae836f92766d9","tid":1441274,"uid":10616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:32:15.000Z","msg":"2014年嘅新聞<br />\n大家千祈唔好廣傳出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n否則會增加警察嘅心理壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】<span style=\"color: gold;\">警務人員</span>工作壓力大，容易<span style=\"color: gold;\">影響家庭生活及婚姻關係</span>，一旦壓力「爆煲」隨時悲劇收場。香港幾乎每年都曾發生<span style=\"color: gold;\">警員自殺</span>事件，有精神科醫生指出，外國研究顯示，<span style=\"color: gold;\">紀律部隊人員</span>、醫護人員、律師等專業人士，屬<span style=\"color: gold;\">自殺</span>的高危一族，因工作要求嚴格，不容錯失，承受壓力極大，更可能影響與伴侶的關係，令其萌生自殺念頭。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20141002/00176_068.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20141002%2F00176_068.html&d=y7g0wjbeyFmnVC7InFCgMmipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=3f26c3ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20141002/00176_068.html</a>"},{"pid":"a8f1dfce57172d2ad9e62187102d7f0ec71d77b1","tid":1441274,"uid":10616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:09:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff9f80da18d81c2b6a55f2b4959c626fe512f1f7","tid":1441274,"uid":144084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:12:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}